{# An AI extended-thinking block surfaced as a collapsible.

   Closed by default (thinking is the model's stream-of-consciousness;
   user opens if curious). Body is markdown-rendered for the same
   reason as ai_message — sub-agents emit thinking in semi-structured
   prose with code spans / lists.

   ctx:
     html  — pre-rendered HTML from render_markdown
#}
<details class="thinking-block">
  <summary class="thinking-summary">Thinking</summary>
  <div class="thinking-body">{{ html|safe }}</div>
</details>
